y country of origin, I was a Navy cadet in a leadership training and development program similar to the Navy Junior Reserve Officer Training Corps, and my dream was to join the Navy.\\\"\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 324, \"end\": 328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\", \"score\": 0.9996267645161828, \"rank\": 0.0002584074367056155, \"text\": \"Navy\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\"}, {\"begin\": 399, \"end\": 441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Junior_Reserve_Officers'_Training_Corps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Navy Junior Reserve Officer Training Corps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Junior_Reserve_Officers'_Training_Corps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Junior_Reserve_Officers'_Training_Corps\"}, {\"begin\": 399, \"end\": 441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Junior_Reserve_Officers'_Training_Corps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Navy Junior Reserve Officer Training Corps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Junior_Reserve_Officers'_Training_Corps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Junior_Reserve_Officers'_Training_Corps\"}, {\"begin\": 472, \"end\": 476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\", \"score\": 0.9996267645161828, \"rank\": 0.0002584074367056155, \"text\": \"Navy\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than 50 Navy sailors will be in Colorado Springs and surrounding areas Monday through Sunday doing volunteer work and meet-and-greet events.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 493, \"end\": 497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\", \"score\": 0.9996267645161828, \"rank\": 0.0002584074367056155, \"text\": \"Navy\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\"}, {\"begin\": 517, \"end\": 525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"score\": 0.9999999048584459, \"rank\": 5.009029278425467e-08, \"text\": \"Colorado\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sailors will also visit Pueblo, Monument, and Woodland Park.\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of them is a Colorado Springs native.\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 708, \"end\": 716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"score\": 0.9999999048584459, \"rank\": 5.009029278425467e-08, \"text\": \"Colorado\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I only met one person in the Navy when I was out here living.\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 796, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 764, \"end\": 768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\", \"score\": 0.9996267645161828, \"rank\": 0.0002584074367056155, \"text\": \"Navy\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have lived in Colorado my whole life.\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 836, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 813, \"end\": 821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"score\": 0.9999999048584459, \"rank\": 5.009029278425467e-08, \"text\": \"Colorado\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I met that one person, he convinced me, and I have loved every minute of it,\\\" said Colorado Springs native and Navy Hull Maintenance Technician Jibreel Scott.\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 1000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 925, \"end\": 933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"score\": 0.9999999048584459, \"rank\": 5.009029278425467e-08, \"text\": \"Colorado\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\"}, {\"begin\": 953, \"end\": 957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\", \"score\": 0.9996267645161828, \"rank\": 0.0002584074367056155, \"text\": \"Navy\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This week, he gets to try and be that one person for someone else, and he says he's happy to be home.\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1103, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I take it very seriously i think it's a special thing to be able to help around the community show people what we do,\\\" Scott said.\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1225, \"end\": 1230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"score\": 0.9338817352205525, \"rank\": 0.07075471849881527, \"text\": \"Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At Monday's event, Vice Admiral John Fuller spoke on Navy Week and why they made the trip to Colorado Springs.\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1270, \"end\": 1281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_W._Fuller\", \"score\": 0.9999700064998486, \"rank\": 2.764559974381879e-05, \"text\": \"John Fuller\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_W._Fuller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_W._Fuller\"}, {\"begin\": 1291, \"end\": 1295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\", \"score\": 0.9996267645161828, \"rank\": 0.0002584074367056155, \"text\": \"Navy\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\"}, {\"begin\": 1331, \"end\": 1339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"score\": 0.9999999048584459, \"rank\": 5.009029278425467e-08, \"text\": \"Colorado\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said it's because of the city's strong military culture, natural beauty, and the hope to educate the community on how the Navy can still impact a landlocked state.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1474, \"end\": 1478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\", \"score\": 0.9996267645161828, \"rank\": 0.0002584074367056155, \"text\": \"Navy\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"90% of international trade goes on the ocean and 95% of data travels through ocean cables,\\\" Fuller said.\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The economy and businesses all in Colorado Springs rely on the Navy, and the Navy's job is to protect the seas, and we thought it was a good fit to at least introduce the Colorado Springs public on the impact the Navy has on their daily lives.\\\"\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\